\n\nEstatal was founded in 1883. It is the oldest university in the city of [[Guayaquil]] and has the largest student body (over 80,000 students). It operates six extension universities throughout the country.{{citation needed|date=November 2013}}\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Ecuador}}\n*[[List of universities in Ecuador]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.ug.edu.ec ug.edu.ec], university's website\n*[http://www.unicarrera.com/universidad/universidad-de-guayaquil-ug] Universidad de Guayaquil\n\n{{coord|-2.18341|-79.89576|display=title}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:University of Guayaquil]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Guayaquil]]\n[[Category:Universities in Ecuador]]\n\n\n{{ecuador-university-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{unreferenced|date=July 2011}}\n{{Expand Spanish|Universidad de Guayaquil|date=March 2010}}\n\n{{Infobox university\n| name              = University of Guayaquil\n| native_name       = ''Universidad de Guayaquil''\n| image             = Universidad de Guayaquil.svg\n| image_name        = \n| image_size        = \n| image_alt         = \n| caption           = \n| latin_name        = \n| motto             = \n| mottoeng          = \n| established       = 1883\n| closed            = \n| type              = [[Public university]]\n| affiliation       = \n| endowment         = \n| budget            = \n| officer_in_charge = \n| chairman          = \n| chancellor        = \n| president         = \n| vice-president    = \n| superintendent    = \n| provost           = \n| vice_chancellor   = \n| rector            = \n| principal         = \n| dean              = \n| director          = \n| head_label        = \n| head              = \n| academic_staff    = \n| administrative_staff  = \n| students          = \n| undergrad         = \n| postgrad          = \n| doctoral          = \n| other             = \n| city              = [[Guayaquil]]\n| state             = \n| province          = [[Guayas Province]]\n|