{"title_page": "University of Guant\u00e1namo", "text_new": "{{Infobox university\n|name            =University Center of Guant\u00e1namo \"CUG\"\n|native_name     =Centro Universitario de Guant\u00e1namo \"CUG\"\n|latin_name      =\n|image           =<!--  Commented out because image was deleted -->\n|motto           =\n|established     =May 28, 1997\n|type            =[[Public university|Public]]\n|endowment       =\n|staff           =\n|rector          =Dr.Cs [[Idania N\u00fa\u00f1ez La O]]\n|students        =\n|undergrad       =\n|postgrad        =\n|doctoral        =\n|city            =[[Guant\u00e1namo]]\n|country         =[[Cuba]]\n|campus          =\n|free_label      =\n|free            =\n|affiliations    =\n|website         =[http://www.cug.co.cu/]\n|logo            =\n}}\n\nThe '''University Center of Guant\u00e1namo''' ({{lang-es|Centro Universitario de Guant\u00e1namo}}, '''CUG''') is a university located in [[Guant\u00e1namo]], [[Cuba]]. It was founded on May 28, 1997<ref>[http://www.cug.co.cu/ Sitio Web]</ref> and is organized in 4 Faculties.<ref>[http://www.cug.co.cu/ Sitio Web]</ref>\n\n==Organization==\n\nThese are the 4 faculties in which the university is divided into:\n\n* Faculty of [[Social Sciences]] and [[Humanities]]<ref>[http://www.ecured.cu/ EcuRed]</ref>\n* Faculty of [[Economy|Economic Sciences]]<ref>[http://www.ecured.cu/ EcuRed]</ref>\n* Faculty of [[Informatics|Informatic Engineering]]<ref>[http://www.ecured.cu/ EcuRed]</ref>\n* Faculty of [[Laws]]<ref>[http://www.ecured.cu/ EcuRed]</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n\n{{Portal|Cuba}}\n*[[Education in Cuba]]\n*[[List of universities in Cuba]]\n* [[Guant\u00e1namo]]\n\n== References ==\n\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.cug.co.cu/ University of Guant\u00e1namo Website] {{in lang|es}}\n\n{{Cub_Uni}}\n\n{{coord missing|Cuba}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:University of Guant\u00e1namo}}\n[[Category:Universities in Cuba|Guant\u00e1namo]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 1997]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Guant\u00e1namo]]\n\n\n{{cuba-university-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox university\n|name            =University Center of Guant\u00e1namo \"CUG\"\n|native_name     =Centro Universitario de Guant\u00e1namo \"CUG\"\n|latin_name      =\n|image           =<!--  Commented out because image was deleted -->\n|motto           =\n|established     =May 28, 1997\n|type            =[[Public university|Public]]\n|endowment       =\n|staff           =\n|rector          =Dr.Cs [[Idania N\u00fa\u00f1ez La O]]\n|students        =\n|undergrad       =\n|postgrad        =\n|doctoral        =\n|city            =[[Guant\u00e1namo]]\n|country         =[[Cuba]]\n|campus          =\n|free_label      =\n|free            =\n|affiliations    =\n|website         =[http://www.cug.co.cu/]\n|logo            =\n}}\n\nThe '''University Center of Guant\u00e1namo''' ({{lang-es|Centro Universitario de Guant\u00e1namo}}, '''CUG''') is a university located in [[Guant\u00e1namo]], [[Cuba]]. It was founded on May 28, 1997<ref>[http://www.cug.co.cu/ Sitio Web]</ref> and is organized in 4 Faculties.<ref>[http://www.cug.co.cu/ Sitio Web]</ref>\n\n==Organization==\n\nThese are the 4 faculties in which the university is divided into:\n\n* Faculty of [[Social Sciences]] and [[Humanities]]<ref>[http://www.ecured.cu/ EcuRed]</ref>\n* Faculty of [[Economy|Economic Sciences]]<ref>[http://www.ecured.cu/ EcuRed]</ref>\n* Faculty of [[Informatics|Informatic Engineering]]<ref>[http://www.ecured.cu/ EcuRed]</ref>\n* Faculty of [[Laws]]<ref>[http://www.ecured.cu/ EcuRed]</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n\n{{Portal|Cuba}}\n*[[Education in Cuba]]\n*[[List of universities in Cuba]]\n* [[Guant\u00e1namo]]\n\n== References ==\n\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.cug.co.cu/ University of Guant\u00e1namo Website] {{in lang|es}}\n\n{{Cub_Uni}}\n\n{{coord missing|Cuba}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:University of Guant\u00e1namo}}\n[[Category:Universities in Cuba|